                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150215-30-victim295 t18150215-30-viclabel171"></join>, belonging the Paddington canel; just before I came to the boat, I saw the prisoner there; I asked my own little boy what business he had there, and when I asked my own little boy, the prisoner put the watch on the top of the bed, I saw him do it; I told the prisoner to come out; he had a shirt in his hat, it fell out, I took the shirt away from him, and had him taken in custody.</p>
